{"tid":2273094,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"很好....你很腦殘嗎....敢這樣講鬼滅之刃.......我死也不會放過你。我給你兩個選擇。","createTime":"2020-11-05T13:11:15.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-16T06:27:32.000Z","uid":13138,"like":42,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"b00b7ded7bfc3796262e6bdd0735533f24f15a89","tid":2273094,"uid":13138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-05T13:11:15.000Z","msg":"很好....你很腦殘嗎....敢這樣講鬼滅之刃.......我死也不會放過你。我給你兩個選擇。<br />\n1:我把你送去給無慘<br />\n2:你給我做好心理準備...因為死亡已經降臨在你身邊了。<br />\n你逼我的，火之神神樂-飛輪陽炎+斜陽轉身+陽華突+圓舞+碧羅天+烈日紅鏡+炎舞+幻日虹<br />\n你給我受死吧:血鬼術:爆血+殺目籠+強制昏睡催眠+濺血鐮+破壞殺+蓮葉冰+寒烈之白姬<br />\n要是敢在這裡再說一次鬼滅之刃油，你就別怪我不客氣了"},{"pid":"4e13871172e9042b3112ff89f78dc06631407dca","tid":2273094,"uid":66952,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-05T13:19:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c8f08bfc273c99ce3a63df886dc3e17facc5aa79","tid":2273094,"uid":120123,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-05T13:19:57.000Z","msg":"好尷尬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"075daf197fe181b14f4cd6945a53ffadb470ba85","tid":2273094,"uid":242244,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-05T13:23:58.000Z","msg":"中二病發？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac30ddee47a6e10c560b1e2d1fd5b5b691ac5126","tid":2273094,"uid":370010,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-05T13:24:59.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"79c18a5ceaf491beac4889e8fb95ca37c8f89ebc","tid":2273094,"uid":256957,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"ac30ddee47a6e10c560b1e2d1fd5b5b691ac5126","tid":2273094,"uid":370010,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-05T13:24:59.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-05T14:19:49.000Z","msg":"很好....你很腦殘嗎....敢這樣講刀劍神域.......我死也不會放過你。我給你兩個選擇。<br />\n1:我把你送去給鬼灯<br />\n2:你給我做好心理準備...因為死亡已經降臨在你身邊了。<br />\n你逼我的，聖使之裝:裝備:聖冥靈武:真-聖星夜嵐靈刀、真-星夜慄凜靈刀<br />\n你給我受死吧:雙刀絕技:奧義，滅靈，賦予亡者戰魂力量，星夜冥靈閃-一式、奧義，聖靈，賦予王者戰魂力量，星夜聖靈閃-二式<br />\n要是敢在這裡再說一次反刀劍神域，你就別怪我不客氣了"},{"pid":"c590ee2c4094846985e5831ba5b6742703dc4918","tid":2273094,"uid":246648,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"ac30ddee47a6e10c560b1e2d1fd5b5b691ac5126","tid":2273094,"uid":370010,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-05T13:24:59.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-05T16:51:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/gpTRuXg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FgpTRuXg.jpg&h=d588b763&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2d4f06f0b345c1a7d07994245e0d695609514e05","tid":2273094,"uid":271250,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-05T16:54:32.000Z","msg":"媽的貢丸"},{"pid":"bd58fff3d50690cc61294084d09e0d2cea82f1b8","tid":2273094,"uid":52073,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-05T17:01:56.000Z","msg":"牛b死了"},{"pid":"dbee0e748ba43d588700d48c1e0d4fe7dfcb2799","tid":2273094,"uid":105678,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-05T17:21:43.000Z","msg":"樓上話好尷尬嗰堆見到都尷尬"},{"pid":"25a6d31a1a210303db2ddd36997c95e2dbfd2083","tid":2273094,"uid":47160,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-05T17:29:04.000Z","msg":"其實啲招名係咪條友自己作<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ef0f8a657483a94e9dcd07e5388344f30eb6b54","tid":2273094,"uid":13138,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-06T03:14:51.000Z","msg":"不客氣了"},{"pid":"7d6f6f5ad82c771150d981b462e1aab3bf26268a","tid":2273094,"uid":26001,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-07T07:52:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />